- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of end-to-end models and external language models for improving ASR performance.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as ASR is a subfield of AI.
- cs.SI (Speech and Audio Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with speech recognition and language modeling.
